---
import { Compass, Grid, MessageSquare } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section id="about" class="pt-[4.8rem] px-6">
  <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto mb-[2.6rem] text-center fade-in">
    <h2 class="text-[2.1rem] tracking-tight mb-[0.6rem] font-bold">How Kunal works</h2>
    <p class="text-[0.98rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.75]">
      From messy problem spaces to quietly confident products, the process stays
      anchored in teams, evidence and thoughtful craft.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-[1.6rem] fade-in">
    
    <article class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="card-body p-6 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0_0,var(--color-base-300),transparent_60%)] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="badge badge-soft gap-1.5 h-auto py-1 px-3 mb-3 relative z-10 shadow-sm">
          <Compass size={14} class="text-primary" />
          Discovery
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="card-title text-[1.15rem] font-semibold mb-2 relative z-10">Make the problem smaller</h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 text-[0.92rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.7]">
          Ground decisions in interviews, flows and data before sketching UI. Aligns
          product, engineering and ops around the same constraints and success
          measures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="card-body p-6 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0_0,var(--color-base-300),transparent_60%)] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="badge badge-soft gap-1.5 h-auto py-1 px-3 mb-3 relative z-10 shadow-sm">
          <Grid size={14} class="text-primary" />
          Systems
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="card-title text-[1.15rem] font-semibold mb-2 relative z-10">Design once, reuse with care</h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 text-[0.92rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.7]">
          Uses systems thinking and shared primitives so new features feel familiar,
          accessible and easy to ship across multiple products.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="card-body p-6 relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0_0,var(--color-base-300),transparent_60%)] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="badge badge-soft gap-1.5 h-auto py-1 px-3 mb-3 relative z-10 shadow-sm">
          <MessageSquare size={14} class="text-primary" />
          Collaboration
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="card-title text-[1.15rem] font-semibold mb-2 relative z-10">Bring teams into the room</h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 text-[0.92rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.7]">
          Coâ€‘creates with PMs, engineers and clinicians through workshops, async
          artifacts and design crits, keeping everyone close to patients.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>
</section>
